  </knowledge>
  <steps>
    <step order="0">Context check + FR-1D.1, FR-1D.2, FR-1D.3, Q3</step>
    <step order="1">Extend MembershipResolverService.ResolveAsync to accept includeRelated[]</step>
    <step order="2">For each related entity, discover its Lookup fields back to the primary entity</step>
    <step order="3">Build chained FetchXML: primary IDs → related IDs</step>
    <step order="4">Extend MembershipResponse.byRole with nested structure (e.g., byRole.documents.{role})</step>
    <step order="5">Update endpoint to parse includeRelated query param</step>
    <step order="6">Reject deeper chains with 400 BadRequest</step>
    <step order="7">Integration tests</step>
  </steps>
  <acceptance-criteria>
